        <list id="id313813" display="block" list-type="enumerated"><item id="uid7">A pulse covers a distance of <m:math><m:mn>5</m:mn><m:mspace width="2pt"/><m:mi mathvariant="normal">m</m:mi></m:math> in <m:math><m:mn>15</m:mn><m:mspace width="2pt"/><m:mi mathvariant="normal">s</m:mi></m:math>. Calculate the speed of the pulse.<newline/><link class="fullmarks" window="new" url="http://www.fhsst.org/l1f">Click here for the solution.</link>
