</item>
          <item id="uid11">The diagram shows two pulses in the same medium. Which has the higher speed? Explain your answer.
<figure id="id313945"><media id="id313945_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/PG10C4_004.png" id="id313945_onlineimage" width="172"><!-- NOTE: attribute width changes image size online (pixels). original width is 152. --></image><image mime-type="application/postscript" for="pdf" src="../../media/PG10C4_004.eps" id="id313945_printimage"/></media></figure><link class="fullmarks" window="new" url="http://www.fhsst.org/l1o">Click here for the solution.</link></item>
        </list>
        
</section>
